ResultDataSet.Name: Port Pair Results By Actual Rx Ports

RealTimeResultGroupDefinition.SqlString: select TxPortName as 'Tx Port', ActualRxPortName as 'Rx Port', sum(TxFrameCount) as 'Tx Count (Frames)', coalesce(sum(FrameCount), 0) as 'Rx Count (Frames)', coalesce(sum(SigFrameCount), 0) as 'Sig Count (Frames)', sum(TxOctetCount * 8) as 'Tx Count (bits)', coalesce(sum(OctetCount * 8), 0) as 'Rx Count (bits)', sum(TxL1BitCount) as 'Tx L1 Count (bits)', coalesce(sum(L1BitCount), 0) as 'Rx L1 Count (bits)', (case when (sum(TxFrameCount) - coalesce(sum(FrameCount), 0)) < 0 then '' else sum(TxFrameCount) - coalesce(sum(FrameCount), 0) end) as 'Tx-Rx (Frames)', (case when (sum(TxFrameCount) - coalesce(sum(FrameCount), 0)) < 0 then '' else round(cast(sum(TxFrameCount) - coalesce(sum(FrameCount), 0) as double) * 100.0 / sum(TxFrameCount), 5) end) as 'Tx-Rx (%)', coalesce(sum(DroppedFrameCount), 0) as 'Dropped Frame Count', round(cast(coalesce(sum(DroppedFrameCount), 0) as double) * 100.0 / sum(TxFrameCount), 5) as 'Dropped Frame(%)', coalesce(sum(InSeqFrameCount), 0) as 'In Sequence Count (Frames)', coalesce(sum(OutSeqFrameCount), 0) as 'Out Sequence Count (Frames)', coalesce(round(cast(sum(TotalLatency) / 100.0 as double) / sum(SigFrameCount), 3), 0.0) as 'Avg Latency(us)', coalesce(min(MinLatency), 0.0) as 'Min Latency (us)', coalesce(max(MaxLatency), 0.0) as 'Max Latency (us)', sum(TxCellCount) as 'Tx Count (Cells)', coalesce(sum(CellCount), 0) as 'Rx Count (Cells)' from TxRxEotStreamResults group by DataSetId, TxParentHnd, ParentHnd
